      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Re-Sounding Poetries: Collections, Classrooms, Communities",
          "textSize": "heading-one"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "In May of 2025, members of the "
        },
        {
          "text": "SpokenWeb SSHRC Partnership",
          "link": "https://spokenweb.ca/"
        },
        {
          "text": " came together at the University of British Columbia Okanagan in Kelowna, BC for the partnership's final annual Sound Institute, entitled "
        },
        {
          "text": "Re-Sounding Poetries: Collections, Classrooms, Communities",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": ". For four days, poets and professors, archivists and artists, librarians and researchers, and creatives of all stripes came together for a \"summer camp\" of immersive literary audio experiences. Information about the Institute and its schedule can be found"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "url": "https://spokenweb.ca/institutes/#/re-sounding-poetries-collections-classrooms-communities",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "here.",
              "link": "https://spokenweb.ca/institutes/#/re-sounding-poetries-collections-classrooms-communities"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "",
          "link": "https://spokenweb.ca/institutes/#/re-sounding-poetries-collections-classrooms-communities"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "SpokenWeb UAlberta in 360°",
          "textSize": "heading-two"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "As part of the SpokenWeb Collections Showcase, where each institution was invited to creatively present on their team's collection, the "
        },
        {
          "text": "University of Alberta SpokenWeb team",
          "link": "https://spokenweb.ualberta.ca/spokenweb-ualberta/"
        },
        {
          "text": " presented a 360° video (sometimes referred to as a virtual reality or VR video) entitled "
        },
        {
          "text": "SpokenWeb UAlberta in 360°",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
